      From timeless paintings to digital masterpieces, our platform celebrates the creativity that makes us human.
    </p>

    <h3><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3064/3064197.png" alt="mission"> What We Do</h3>
    <p>
      We offer a curated gallery for showcasing unique artworks, support emerging artists to share their vision, and help art enthusiasts discover and own pieces they love.
      Beyond selling art, our goal is to create meaningful connections between creators and appreciators.
    </p>

